</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Hankins" box="[495,819,1707,1733]" pageId="6" pageNumber="61" refString="Hankins, A. &amp; Baldwin, C. C. (2002) How Many Blennies is the Redlip Blenny? Research Training Program, Poster Session, Smithsonian Museum. Available from http: // www. nmnh. si. edu / rtp / students / 2002 / virtualposterinfo / poster _ 2002 _ hankins. htm (accessed 8 may 2008)" type="journal article" year="2002">
